## ğŸ§  Quick Glossary (Beginner-Friendly)

- **Repository (Repo):** Your project folder on GitHub (files + history).
- **Commit:** A saved change (â€œsnapshotâ€ of your project).
- **Branch:** A safe copy of your repo where you can experiment.
- **Pull Request (PR):** A request to merge your branch changes into `main`.
- **Merge:** Applying your branch changes to `main`.
- **main:** The default branch (your â€œofficialâ€ version).

