# 8ï¸âƒ£ Verify Everything on main

1. Go back to the **Code** tab.
2. Switch branch dropdown back to `main`
3. Confirm:
   - README changes are visible
   - New files are there
   - Commit history shows a merge commit

âœ… Youâ€™re done â€” this is the basic GitHub workflow.

