## ğŸ§¯ Troubleshooting (Quick Fixes)

- **I donâ€™t see my changes**
  - Make sure youâ€™re viewing the `main` branch (branch dropdown).
- **My PR canâ€™t merge**
  - This usually means â€œconflicts.â€ Keep edits small and avoid changing the same lines in different places.
- **README formatting looks weird**
  - Confirm the file is named `README.md`
  - Use headings consistently (`#`, `##`, `###`)

